    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric sci-fi adventure in a post-human world</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are The Designer. Once a brilliant roboticist, now an old man who woke up after 30 years in hibernation. Your facility: ruined. Your wife: vanished. Your memory: a mess. Robots that once served you developed personalities and started obeying a central AI called The Mainframe. They seem determined to stop you from discovering the truth and to put you back to sleep. Don't let them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/99c1fc0827bb454ba09a02ea0b5c2c6c.poster.avif?t=1757512158\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/99c1fc0827bb454ba09a02ea0b5c2c6c.webm?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/99c1fc0827bb454ba09a02ea0b5c2c6c.mp4?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-time tactical stealth gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your hacking tool and robot companions to evade, distract and maneuver enemies and outsmart the evil AI that has corrupted your facility. The environment you once called home is yours to command - if you manage to take back control while remaining unseen ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/faaded2062805eebe211008b7a99cf31.poster.avif?t=1757512158\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/faaded2062805eebe211008b7a99cf31.webm?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/faaded2062805eebe211008b7a99cf31.mp4?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party members with unique personalities and skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble a party of distinct robots with unique abilities and take control of them to compensate for your own deteriorating body. Recruit a cynical NurseBot, a fearless CleanerBot, a chipper SecurityBot and a loyal HunterBot in a robot version of Ocean's Eleven where you're the entire team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/7aa2e905653bb503f295776a80cd3301.poster.avif?t=1757512158\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/7aa2e905653bb503f295776a80cd3301.webm?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145980/extras/7aa2e905653bb503f295776a80cd3301.mp4?t=1757512158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
